        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Rescinding DHS' Waiver Authority for Border Wall Act</strong></p> <p>This bill rescinds the authority of the Department of Homeland Security to waive legal requirements in order to ensure the expeditious construction of barriers and roads in the vicinity of the U.S. border.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
